<p>Christian NH Hauemann a physician of the city of St Louis do hereby certify that I have at diverse times and last <unclear></unclear> the day of Dec 1867 seen and examined Caroline Bauer wife of John Bauer of the city and county of St Louis and believe said Caroline Bauer to suffer of monomania and a proper patient to <unclear>be read</unclear> to the State luncatic asylum</p>

